overview.en: HBO (H-bond) is used for private placement according to the plan 10%, subscribed by Genesis nodes; 5% is used for operation promotion; 10% is held by the foundation; 5% is held by the technology development team; Ecological application and mining.
overview.cn: HBO（H-bond）根据规划10%用于私募，由创世节点认购；5%用于运营推广；10%由基金会持有；5%由技术开发团队持有；剩余70%则用于生态应用及挖矿。
